<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03134f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03134f">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03134f"> 134(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> delight (shell)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[letter from Mrs PC&apos;s son]</font>: The mortars are fine, and we fire a <mark>shell</mark> about the size of St. Paul&apos;s, which make a noise like an earthquake. I direct their fire from the nearest point of the enemy. Our Tommies love them, and the cry is ever&mdash;&lsquo;Give &apos;em some more &ldquo;<mark>Delight,&rdquo; Sir!</mark>&rsquo; <small> Mrs Patrick Campbell, <a name="PCML" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#PCML"><cite title="source">My Life and Some Letters</cite></a> (1922) 388</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
